Blaine.Andover, Minnesota:
Andover is a city in Anoka County, Minnesota, United States. The population was 30,598 at the 2010 census.


== Geography ==
According to the United States Census Bureau, the city has a total area of 34.83 square miles (90.21 km2), of which, 33.88 square miles (87.75 km2) is land and 0.95 square miles (2.46 km2) is water.
